for the most of these scripts, Vim 6.x required.

syntax files that modify existing settings should go into:

    after/syntax/

new syntax files should be placed into:

    syntax/

to install, link `vimrc' file to `.vimrc' in your home directory:

    % ln vimrc ~/.vimrc
    % ln gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
    % ln viewrc ~/.viewrc

install `vless' somewhere within your $PATH or create shell alias like this:    

    % alias vs=~/.vim/vless

